717747f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 134th Street (West)
717747f-a.text:
Broadway, south from but not inclcding West 134th Street, showing
the street in preparation for repa4ing. On the right, partially obscured
by steam boiler is a 3-story brick house at the N.W. corner of West 133rd
Street and south of it.a 5-story one,bearing No. 3289 Broadway, between
West 133rd and West 132nd Streets.
June 30, 1900.
Board of Transportation Photograph.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
William B. Parsons Collection.
